        "title": "2D Falicov--Kimball Model with Correlated Hopping in the Large U Limit",
        "abstract": "Two-dimensional spinless Falicov-Kimball model with correlated hopping is studied perturbatively in the limit of large on-site Coulomb interaction U. In the neutral case the effective Hamiltonian in spin variables is derived up to terms proportional to U^-3. The ground-state phase diagram of the effective Hamiltonian is examined in the (a/t, h) plane, where a/t is a parameter characterizing strength of the correlated hopping and h is a difference of chemical potentials.",
